{"tid":1649911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蛋糕女要起底嚴肅處理，但行動post更重要!!!","createTime":"2019-10-12T18:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T19:15:55.000Z","uid":312692,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c267ada6328ab9e7e0b75bb7e92f3f3c69c82c9f","tid":1649911,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:57:52.000Z","msg":"呢件事己經起咗苗頭<br />\n代表日後發生同類事件機會更大<br />\n隨時瓦解成場運動<br />\n<br />\n我並非強調必須苦行<br />\n但呢啲侮辱、唔尊重既on9野唔可以再發生<br />\n要<span style=\"color: red;\">以儆效尤</span><br />\n<br />\nanyway<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">聽日同後日集中呢三個活動</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZH7cNeH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZH7cNeH.jpg&h=8274e20a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好因為條八婆而忽視目標</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e65873ccdb30cf9b6fa9004b23fd9e18e199ccf5","tid":1649911,"uid":89903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c267ada6328ab9e7e0b75bb7e92f3f3c69c82c9f","tid":1649911,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:57:52.000Z","msg":"呢件事己經起咗苗頭<br />\n代表日後發生同類事件機會更大<br />\n隨時瓦解成場運動<br />\n<br />\n我並非強調必須苦行<br />\n但呢啲侮辱、唔尊重既on9野唔可以再發生<br />\n要<span style=\"color: red;\">以儆效尤</span><br />\n<br />\nanyway<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">聽日同後日集中呢三個活動</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZH7cNeH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZH7cNeH.jpg&h=8274e20a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好因為條八婆而忽視目標</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8zncNfG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8zncNfG.jpg&h=c99dbf1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BAfBut1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBAfBut1.png&h=55ec2194&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d4502e821c41a77a3b65052605d57dc810d754a","tid":1649911,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:58:45.000Z","msg":"《人手轉載》<br />\n<br />\n希望大家維持嗌五大訴求：<br />\n1.缺一不可本來就有環環相扣既意思，正如林鄭撤回咗條例，都唔會改嗌四大訴求，簡單啲講，呢句野既結果一係5，一係0，冇其他。<br />\n2.解散警隊呢個訴求並唔夠實際同具體，基本上五大訴求達成就已經可以蓋括埋解散警隊既效果，正如一開始第五個訴求係林鄭下台，大家都覺得呢個訴求唔實際，所以改做雙普選，所以，我地係唔需要特登加多一個訴求落去，咁先比到人睇我地一直爭取緊既係具體、可行、實際既訴求。<br />\n解散警隊可以獨立嗌，代表我地對警隊嚴重不滿，但唔好將佢當做第六大訴求。<br />\n3.國際啱啱先開始知到我地爭取緊既係五大訴求而唔係林鄭一句撤回就咁簡單，所以維持五大訴求先比到人一種由始此終都係爭取緊同一樣野既觀感。"},{"pid":"d78b7700c67d43f7647bcb8fef916e46915b4f43","tid":1649911,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:58:45.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"33c67cfc5beb9008645760281d0df32a39c344d5","tid":1649911,"uid":129803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:59:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e98ea2583e606dfe499cbe01ac3f1cab17b3319","tid":1649911,"uid":13873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:59:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3da2a5ee4a694acc1011f2384f20c6b687762a35","tid":1649911,"uid":135349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wERQyWc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwERQyWc.jpg&h=51c56c27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c81b659de84d6837afaf39e229a2f2a85617ff6a","tid":1649911,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:00:02.000Z","msg":"起條撚咩 你搞完佢又可以點"},{"pid":"8439a585256